218
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,280
Even though it’s my mom’s money.

219
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:20,280
So the only thing that I want…

220
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:21,960
It’s you.

221
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:27,960
You, you, you, you.

222
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,960
